ings sections are s2, s3, s4.\n\nNow I'm extracting the section content. s1 contains the XML config example showing the full setup with SimpleDbTransactionManager, BasicStringResourceLoader with its properties like dbManager and tableName, and StringResourceHolder configured with BasicStaticDataCache. For s2, I'm looking at the StringResourceHolder property table that details the stringResourceCache configuration. I'm setting up the XML configuration for the database transaction manager and string resource loader, then configuring the string resource holder to use a cache for storing the loaded messages. Now I'm looking at the BasicStaticDataCache configuration details and how it relates to the StringResourceHolder setup, then moving into the BasicStringResourceLoader class which requires a database manager and table name to load messages from the database. 次に、SimpleDbTransactionManager、messageResourceコンポーネント、DBメッセージ設定の例を確認してから、StringResourceHolderの設定方法を見ていく。その後、BasicStaticDataCacheとBasicStringResourceLoaderの各クラスの設定について詳しく説明する必要がある。\n\nBasicStringResourceLoaderではdbManager、tableName、idColumnName、langColumnName、valueColumnNameといったテーブル設定パラメータが重要になってくる。最後に、公式ドキュメントのURLを確認したが、ベースURLが空なので、参照配列は空になる。","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21037,"cache_read_input_tokens":29889,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":21037,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"258acb25-a395-47c8-99e6-3e6ccc7658e7","uuid":"e2b93a5e-2d59-4b84-8d7d-efbec2541c6d"}
